Assistant Sales Product Manager
Responsibilities
Promote company product and services by creating an opportunities from customer’s need and company’s product and services.Work with service operation team to ensure product and services are delivered as per customer expectation.Maintains all sales systems, such as sales records and reports, conference calendar, traces of history and potentials, logs of groups not previously accommodated and mailing lists.Monitoring  the progress of projects and ensuring customers problem are addressed with related parties both internal and external.Responsible to deliver sales quota as per  company’s expected both to current and or new customer.Assists in the creation of the Marketing and Sales plans. Requirements Diploma or Bachelor’s degree (Engineering - Computer/Telecommunication - Marketing or equivalent)Minimum of 2 year experience as a SalesHaving experience in distribution company Excellent written and verbal communication skillsExcellent teamwork skillsExcellent in English
